- Canonical URLs
- Schema markup for portfolio items

Task 2: Meta Tags & Social Sharing

Perfect social sharing:
- Custom Open Graph images for each section
- Twitter Card optimization
- Proper descriptions for each page/section
- Preview how it looks on social platforms

Task 3: Analytics Integration

Add Google Analytics:
- Set up GA4
- Track key events (form submissions, portfolio clicks, CTA clicks)
- Add to app/layout.tsx
- Create lib/analytics.ts for event tracking

Task 4: Schema & Local SEO (if applicable)

Add LocalBusiness schema:
- Business location
- Hours of operation
- Contact information
- Service areas
- Reviews aggregate
